{"tid":1732884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"齊救理大","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T03:40:56.000Z","uid":318973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef7e8d3720810456a2199f50e9d7fa47211bfd4e","tid":1732884,"uid":318973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:40:18.000Z","msg":"依家尖嘴有好多手足聚緊<br />\n但系依家班狗嘅目的似乎系將poly入面嘅手足當人質<br />\n引外面嘅手足出黎 之後圍捕一次過拉曬<br />\n同埋依家出面有攻唔到入去<br />\n入面有攻唔翻出黎<br />\n所以希望有手足可以去包圍翻狗舍火攻狗舍<br />\n挾持翻啲狗嘅家屬 逼拒地回防<br />\n因為依家大部分狗都出左去<br />\n得翻少量便衣狗系狗舍"},{"pid":"af7324cb02664c2d0d84260e65dbc54e159a6d5a","tid":1732884,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9ZjRtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9ZjRtg.jpg&h=edebd45e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n緊急呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去佐敦啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"}]}